&lt;li&gt;Enhance the performance, reliability, scalability, and throughput of real-time trading systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with quantitative researchers to improve the profitability and effectiveness of trading strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
